description: Havsfrun Investment AB engages in the provision of investment services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 5 full-time employees.  As of December 31, 2011, the Company’s investment portfolio comprised of Multi Strategy Funds, Global Macro Funds, Equity Long/Short Funds, Credit Funds and Event Driven Funds, among others. As of December 31, 2011, the Company had two wholly owned subsidiaries, namely Havsfrun Capital AB, located in Sweden and Havsfrun SA, located in Luxembourg.
naicsSubsector: Securities, Commodity Contracts, and Other Financial Investments and Related Activities
